<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/mycokeys.98.106240.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Phylogram based on the Maximum Likelihood (ML) analysis using the SSU, ITS, LSU, RPB 2 and EF 1 A sequences of Clavicipitaceae. The ML bootstrap values (≥ 70 %) and the Bayesian posterior probability values (≥ 0.70) are indicated along the branches (BP / ML). The new taxa are highlighted in bold." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/860996" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

